---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, GAME_NAME, EVIDENCE_REVIEW_DATE } from '../data/site';
---

<ContentLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Demon Born Compass — an unofficial fan guide for Demon Born Roblox."
  canonicalUrl="/about/"
>
  <h1>About {SITE_TITLE}</h1>

  <p>
    <strong>{SITE_TITLE}</strong> is an unofficial fan guide for <strong>{GAME_NAME}</strong> on Roblox.
    It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to Roblox Corporation, SoraExp, or any
    Demon Born creators.
  </p>

  <div class="info-block">
    <strong>What this site does:</strong>
    <ul style="margin-top: var(--space-3); margin-bottom: 0">
      <li>Tracks official source status for wiki, Trello, and codes</li>
      <li>Publishes only officially confirmed game facts</li>
      <li>Lists controls directly from the Roblox game description</li>
      <li>Maintains a full source registry with claim IDs</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="info-block" style="border-left-color: var(--color-warning-text); background: var(--color-warning-bg)">
    <strong>What this site does not do:</strong>
    <ul style="margin-top: var(--space-3); margin-bottom: 0">
      <li>No tier lists, best builds, best clans, or best breathing styles</li>
      <li>No codes copied from Pocket Tactics, Destructoid, Beebom, Radio Times, or other third-party sites</li>
      <li>No claims about official Trello or Discord unless a verified official link is provided</li>
      <li>No unofficial screenshots, Roblox media, or competitor content</li>
      <li>No breathing styles, blood demon arts, or clan mechanics (not yet confirmed from official sources)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2>Why this site exists</h2>
  <p>
    Google Trends and SERP observations supplied by the operator show rising interest in
    <em>Demon Born wiki</em>, <em>Demon Born trello</em>, and <em>Demon Born codes</em>.
    The current SERP for these queries is mixed — unrelated pages, code aggregators, and one
    exact-match competitor wiki appear, but no authoritative, evidence-backed hub exists yet.
  </p>
  <p>
    This site fills that gap with a lightweight, official-source-only approach while the game
    is still in its early (World Cup Beta) stage.
  </p>

  <h2>Evidence and updates</h2>
  <p>
    All game facts are tied to claim IDs that map to source IDs in the
    <a href="/sources/">Sources registry</a>. Evidence was last reviewed on
    <strong>{EVIDENCE_REVIEW_DATE}</strong>. Pages are not updated automatically —
    each change is reviewed and versioned.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    To report a factual error, submit a correction, or flag a broken link,
    use the <a href="/contact/">Contact</a> page. Corrections are reviewed against
    official sources before any page is updated.
  </p>

  <h2>Ads and tracking</h2>
  <p>
    This site has no advertisements, no analytics scripts, and no tracking cookies.
    It is currently a static preview deployed to Vercel. No custom domain has been purchased.
  </p>
</ContentLayout>